IMAPStore astrophotography-proton-remote
   Port 1143
   Host 127.0.0.1
   User astrofotografie@protonmail.com
   PassCmd "bash ~/.scripts/get-pw.sh ~/.config/mbsync/crypt-store/astrophotography-proton"
   TLSType NONE
   CertificateFile ~/.config/mbsync/certs/proton-bridge.pem

MaildirStore astrophotography-proton-local
   SubFolders Verbatim
   Path ~/Mail/astrophotography-proton/
   Inbox ~/Mail/astrophotography-proton/Inbox

Channel astrophotography-proton
   Far :astrophotography-proton-remote:
   Near :astrophotography-proton-local:
   Patterns * !Labels* !"All Mail"
   Create Both
   Expunge Both
   SyncState *

